      <title>加州工作场所安全委员会批准室内工人（监狱除外）的防暑措施</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/heat-indoor-workers-protections-california-9ed0ee9f5d38a30f1318e50b954c0936</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州工作场所监管机构通过了保护室内工人免受高温影响的法规。该法规将适用于仓库、学校和厨房等工作场所。]]></description>
      <guid>https://apnews.com/article/heat-indoor-workers-protections-california-9ed0ee9f5d38a30f1318e50b954c0936</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 00:23:18 GMT</pubDate>
